0:07:21.460,0:07:25.060
Those chains were just tightening - very tight.

0:07:25.060,0:07:28.440
He started breaking the chains in the name of Jesus.

0:07:28.440,0:07:35.140
Shall we put our hands together for Christ Jesus!

0:07:35.140,0:07:38.180
When he broke the chain, he gave me the key.

0:07:38.180,0:07:44.020
He said, "Take this key. This is the room that tied your destiny. Now it is over!

0:07:44.020,0:07:48.620
I shouted, "God, thank You! Jesus, thank You!"

0:07:48.620,0:07:52.680
